;; DEMO: all the rate buckets at once — a stress test for FA(3)
;; P_13_N/P_14_N routing. One line per bucket:
;;
;;   23%   → P_13_1 / P_14_1   (std)
;;   8%    → P_13_2 / P_13_2   (red1)
;;   5%    → P_13_3 / P_14_3   (red2)
;;   0 KR  → P_13_6_1          (domestic zero)
;;   :zw   → P_13_7            (exempt)
;;   :np   → P_13_8            (np I, art. 28b)
;;   :np-eu → P_13_9           (np II, art. 100)
;;
;; This is the "did the bucket router lose a line?" regression guard.
;; Buyer is PL → Podmiot2 emits <NIP>; the :np/:np-eu items coexist
;; with PL-domestic rates in the same invoice, so the DodatkowyOpis
;; block must surface both legal-basis entries.

